data.description: Nestled within serene surroundings, this beautiful log home is a haven of warmth and character. Boasting three bedrooms, two baths, and a wealth of inviting features, this residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and rustic charm. The main living area seamlessly combines the kitchen, dining, and living spaces, creating an open and inviting atmosphere for entertaining or daily living comfort.Additional perks to the property include; - 400 gallons of propane filled January 22nd!  - Clear views of the auroras when they're out! - Wildlife year round! - Quiet neighborhood at the end of a cul-de-sac with no through traffic! - Gravel laid along entire driveway in 2022 so there's no mud during breakup! - Established garden area with recurring strawberries, raspberries, and rhubarb! - Large established red apple tree that puts out a ton of apples annually! - 3 crab apple trees, 1 established, 2 from 2023.  All 3 put out a ton of crab apples annually.  (Great for applesauce, apple butter, jellies, etc.) - Just a few blocks from Bear Paw Lake for year round fun!
